Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteAllScanCells(25.10)                            deleteAllScanCells(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllScanCells - Unassigns all assigned scan cells

Syntax
       deleteAllScanCells

       [-help]

       Unassigns all assigned scan cells. This command can be called after im-
       porting the design if there are scan cell specifications in library; or
       else it can be used after the specifyScanCell command.

Parameters
       None

Example
       The  following set of commands deletes all scan cells after loading de-
       sign:

       restoreDesign init.enc.dat top

        deleteAllScanCells

Related Information
              * Placing the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

                * Optimizing and Reordering Scan Chains

